543
00:22:34,977 --> 00:22:35,976
and we get his back.

544
00:22:36,095 --> 00:22:37,061
Yeah.

545
00:22:37,146 --> 00:22:39,096
Maybe he'll even hire
us at his new company.

546
00:22:40,182 --> 00:22:41,565
Flutterbeam.

547
00:22:48,824 --> 00:22:50,741
- Mustaches?
- Yes.

548
00:22:50,826 --> 00:22:53,410
Doesn't necessarily
have to stop at people.

549
00:22:53,496 --> 00:22:55,329
They can put mustaches
on their pets, too.

550
00:22:55,448 --> 00:22:56,780
It's actually pretty fun.

551
00:22:56,916 --> 00:23:01,285
So, soon you'll be putting
mustaches on cats and dogs and...

552
00:23:01,370 --> 00:23:03,287
- snakes.
- Snakes, yeah, yeah.

553
00:23:03,422 --> 00:23:06,040
I mean, it's a little tricky because
they don't have a philtrum,

554
00:23:06,125 --> 00:23:10,544
so finding an anchor point for
that mustache is actually...

555
00:23:10,630 --> 00:23:13,764
gonna be quite of a
technological challenge.

556
00:23:13,849 --> 00:23:15,466
- It's exciting stuff.
- It really is.

557
00:23:15,551 --> 00:23:16,717
Richard.

558
00:23:16,802 --> 00:23:18,602
Let me ask you something.

559
00:23:19,472 --> 00:23:21,221
Why are you leaving Pied Piper?

560
00:23:23,859 --> 00:23:25,893
They pushed me out.

561
00:23:25,978 --> 00:23:27,444
I thought they offered
you another position.

562
00:23:27,530 --> 00:23:29,813
Yeah, CTO. It's a demotion.

563
00:23:29,949 --> 00:23:32,232
Well, wouldn't you be
CTO at Flutterbeam?

564
00:23:32,318 --> 00:23:35,986
Yes, but at least this way,
I don't have to eat shit.

565
00:23:36,122 --> 00:23:39,573
Richard, let me tell you something
I learned here on the inside.

566
00:23:41,077 --> 00:23:45,913
Swallow your pride, or soon you'll be
eating something far worse than shit.

567
00:23:46,916 --> 00:23:48,716
Believe me.

568
00:23:48,834 --> 00:23:52,836
Don't you think you should at
least meet this Barker fellow?

569
00:23:53,756 --> 00:23:54,722
(SIGHS)

570
00:23:54,840 --> 00:23:57,007
- ♪
♪
- (MURMURING)

