anyway you see fit.

575
00:24:15,578 --> 00:24:18,912
Employee bonuses, renovations
to the day-care center.

576
00:24:19,031 --> 00:24:21,615
What have you. What
should we prioritize?

577
00:24:25,538 --> 00:24:27,171
BIG HEAD: <i>Sorry, I don't understand.</i>

578
00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:29,707
It's all in the document.

579
00:24:29,842 --> 00:24:31,592
You take that severance package,

580
00:24:31,711 --> 00:24:34,678
and you leave Hooli immediately.

581
00:24:34,764 --> 00:24:36,463
But the most important aspect

582
00:24:36,549 --> 00:24:39,717
is the non-disclosure,
non-disparagement clause,

583
00:24:39,852 --> 00:24:44,221
in which you agree not to say
anything negative in the press,

584
00:24:44,306 --> 00:24:46,557
in public, or in private

585
00:24:46,692 --> 00:24:48,892
about Hooli or Gavin Belson.

586
00:24:49,779 --> 00:24:51,862
Okay, I won't.

587
00:24:51,947 --> 00:24:54,031
You will not discuss
anything you did at Hooli

588
00:24:54,116 --> 00:24:57,368
at all, in perpetuity,

589
00:24:57,453 --> 00:24:58,485
throughout the universe.

590
00:24:58,571 --> 00:25:01,288
I didn't really do
anything at Hooli, so...

591
00:25:01,407 --> 00:25:03,707
Good. You're getting the
hang of it already.

592
00:25:03,793 --> 00:25:05,709
So, can I keep my Hooli ID, though,

593
00:25:05,795 --> 00:25:08,879
so I can still come and hang out
with my friends on the roof?

594
00:25:08,964 --> 00:25:10,547
You cannot.

595
00:25:10,633 --> 00:25:13,300
Officially, you will no
longer have any friends here.

596
00:25:13,419 --> 00:25:14,418
Shoot.

597
00:25:15,805 --> 00:25:18,172
I have to think about this then.

598
00:25:18,257 --> 00:25:21,425
This settlement offer is quite generous.

599
00:25:21,510 --> 00:25:25,262
I know, I know. I mean, $2
million is a lot of money.

600
00:25:26,232 --> 00:25:28,682
Two? No. It's...

601
00:25:29,819 --> 00:25:31,935
It's $20 million.

602
00:25:34,690 --> 00:25:35,856
Twenty?

603
00:25:40,613 --> 00:25:43,080
So they fired me before they hired you,

604
00:25:43,165 --> 00:25:45,365
so it's not your fault. I just...

605
00:25:45,451 --> 00:25:48,452
I feel like this... can't really work.

606
00:25:48,537 --> 00:25:50,003
- Do you understand?
- I do, Richard.

607
00:25:50,122 --> 00:25:51,338
It's like...

608
00:25:51,457 --> 00:25:54,425
can I really be expected
to do my best work

609
00:25:54,510 --> 00:25:57,211
